Document - Class in com.procom.filefly.model
Models the properties of transmitted files/documents for the purpose of storing the information in a Collection for easy access by such classes as DocumentListFragment.

DocumentListAdapter - Class in com.procom.filefly
The android.widget.BaseAdapter used to back the ListView hosted by the DocumentListFragment using Documents as the data model.

DocumentListFragment - Class in com.procom.filefly
The Fragment that establishes the user interface for the android.widget.ListView by connecting to a SQLite database in internal storage and constructing a List of Documents managed by a android.widget.BaseAdapter from the queried data.
